# 301 redirect map for the Odoo → Astro migration.
# Format: Netlify / Cloudflare Pages `_redirects`. The trailing `301!` forces
# the redirect even if a file exists. Old paths below are the real indexed
# Odoo URLs from Google Search Console (Pages export).
#
# LAUNCH BLOCKER (only relevant once the site moves to packetflow.be): without
# these, the ranking + backlink equity of the old URLs is lost.

# ---- Canonical host: keep www (the host Odoo ranks on), 301 the apex ----
https://packetflow.be/*   https://www.packetflow.be/:splat   301!

# ---- Old Odoo paths → new equivalents (from GSC) ----
/diensten/it-beheer        /diensten/it-beheer-support           301   # 493 impressions
/kmo-pakket                /pakket                               301   # 377 impressions
/diensten/wifi-netwerk     /diensten/zakelijke-wifi-netwerken    301
/sectoren/vrije-beroepen   /sectoren/kantoren-vrije-beroepen     301
/contactus                 /contact                              301
/appointment/1             /contact                              301   # Odoo appointment page

# English pages → Dutch equivalents (site is nl-only now)
/en/about-me               /over-mij                             301
/en/privacy                /privacy                              301
/en/*                      /                                     301

# Unchanged slugs (/, /over-mij, /privacy) need no redirect.
#
# NOTE: lab.packetflow.be (homelab) is a separate subdomain — out of scope here.
